                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Short-Term</div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed font-light">
                        Valid for <strong class="text-slate-900">&lt; 1 year</strong>. Often tied to a specific project. Hard to renew for Non-EU.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Permit B -->
                <div class="bg-slate-900 p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-800 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#FF6F61]/5 blur-[60px]"></div>
                    <div class="text-6xl font-black text-[#FF6F61] mb-8 relative z-10">B</div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 relative z-10">Residence</div>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed font-light relative z-10">
                        The gold standard. Valid for <strong class="text-white">5 years (EU)</strong> or <strong class="text-white">1 year (Non-EU)</strong>. Renewable annually.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Permit C -->
                <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-[#FF6F61]/30 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
                    <div class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-100 mb-8 group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">C</div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Settlement</div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed font-light">
                        Permanent residency. Granted after 5-10 years. Near-citizenship rights including open job mobility.
                    </p>
                </div>

                 <!-- Permit G -->
                 <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-[#FF6F61]/30 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 group">
                    <div class="text-6xl font-black text-slate-100 mb-8 group-hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors">G</div>
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Cross-Border</div>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-base leading-relaxed font-light">
                        For cross-border commuters living in EU border zones (DE/FR/IT) returning at least weekly.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. "The Ecosystem Advantage" (Rounded Comparison) -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-24 items-center">
