                    </p>
                    
                    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 text-sm">
                            <CheckCircle2 className="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" />
                            <span>Detailed Quota Analysis & Strategy</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 text-sm">
                            <CheckCircle2 className="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" />
                            <span>Legal-Grade Document Review</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 text-sm">
                            <CheckCircle2 className="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 shrink-0" />
                            <span>Priority Cantonal Liaison</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <a href="/search/results?service=visa-immigration" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full py-4 bg-[#FF6F61] text-white text-center font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-[#e5574d] rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl no-underline">
                        Find Your Specialist Now <ArrowRight className="w-4 h-4 ml-2" />
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. Why Use a Relocation Agency for Immigration -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Why Use an Agency?</h2>
                <div class="h-1.5 w-24 bg-[#FF6F61] mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
